### Run the pipeline — rows flow source → target over HTTP.
POST http://localhost:4104/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ShipmentArchive","mode":"delta","trigger":"manual"}

### Verify the archive now has rows (remote target, remote query).
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/ShipmentArchive?$orderby=archivedAt desc&$top=10

### Second run — UPSERT keeps the target idempotent.
POST http://localhost:4104/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ShipmentArchive","mode":"delta","trigger":"manual"}

### Full refresh — O(n) remote DELETEs. Only useful on small targets.
POST http://localhost:4104/pipeline/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"ShipmentArchive","mode":"full","trigger":"manual"}
